---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL === '/' ? '/' : import.meta.env.BASE_URL + '/';
---

<section class="section spotlight">
  <div class="container spotlight__inner">
    <div class="spotlight__visual reveal">
      <div class="spotlight__image-wrapper">
        <img 
          src={`${base}images/speakers/rosamira-guillen.jpg`} 
          alt="Rosamira Guillén - Ponente Magistral" 
          class="spotlight__img"
        />
        <div class="spotlight__badge">
          <span class="badge badge-natgeo">National Geographic Explorer</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="spotlight__content">
      <div class="spotlight__header reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
        <span class="section-label">Ponente Magistral Confirmada</span>
        <h2 class="spotlight__title">Rosamira Guillén</h2>
        <p class="spotlight__subtitle">Directora Ejecutiva de la Fundación Proyecto Tití</p>
      </div>

      <div class="spotlight__body reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
        <p>
          Arquitecta y conservacionista colombiana, líder en la protección del <strong>Tití Cabeciblanco</strong>. Su labor ha sido reconocida internacionalmente con el prestigioso <strong>Whitley Award (2015)</strong> y el <strong>National Geographic Buffett Award (2017)</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          En el III Congreso Peruano de Primatología, Rosamira compartirá su experiencia liderando estrategias integrales que combinan ciencia, desarrollo comunitario y educación ambiental para salvar a una de las especies de primates más amenazadas del mundo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="spotlight__footer reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
        <div class="spotlight__highlights">
          <div class="spotlight__highlight">
            <span class="highlight-icon">🌍</span>
            <span class="highlight-text">Liderazgo Internacional</span>
          </div>
          <div class="spotlight__highlight">
            <span class="highlight-icon">🐒</span>
            <span class="highlight-text">Conservación de Especies</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .spotlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--forest-darkest) 0%, #4a2b11 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 6rem 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .spotlight__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .spotlight__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
      gap: 5rem;
    }
  }

  /* ── Visual ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .spotlight__visual {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .spotlight__image-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 450px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(217,157,85,0.2);
  }

  .spotlight__img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    transition: transform var(--transition-slow);
  }

  .spotlight__image-wrapper:hover .spotlight__img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .spotlight__badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 1.5rem;
    left: 1.5rem;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .badge-natgeo {
    background: #FFCC00;
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  /* ── Content ─────────────────────────────────────── */
  .spotlight__content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .spotlight__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .spotlight__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .spotlight__body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .spotlight__body p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  }

  .spotlight__body strong {
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  /* ── Footer ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .spotlight__highlights {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .spotlight__highlight {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(217,157,85,0.15);
  }

  .highlight-icon { font-size: 1.25rem; }
  
  .highlight-text {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
</style>
